Breakfast for a hc vegan. I have to go see a nutritionist today. I hate it. The people on my Snapchat knows what happens, but I'll say it again for the people who don't. I'm starting this stupid therapy thing for people who have eating disorders. I don't know what you want to call it, but I don't have an eating disorder. I guess if you lose weight and you don't like what you look like you have an eating disorder. Anyways I go there like every day. But the sucky thing is, is that it goes all the way from after school, to 8pm. That is going to screw with my homework and studying time. Anyways it's this group thing that kids ages 12-18 come together and do, "feeling," activities. I have a feeling I'm not going to make any friends. And I don't plan too. We all know what the workers there want to do to us. And it ain't nice. Also, we eat dinner and snacks there. The thing that is really fucking bullshit, is that they are making me eat meat, dairy, eggs, etc. the girl who talked to me about it said, "we don't honor vegetarians and vegans! This is a recovery so we will be making you eat meat and dairy." WTF?! Have a little flexibility!! Anyways I'm going to a nutritionist today and I'm going to try to talk her into letting me eat vegan. THE SNACKS REQUIRE A DAIRY PRODUCT. good thing that there's like 3 snacks that aren't from animals. But there super high in fat and sugar. Also, last thing. There's this form that I have to fill out about allergies. Hopefully they will believe me when I write down I'm allergic to fish, milk, eggs, and dairy.
